    • Method Detail

      • style

        public <E> E style(E element,
          Object data)
        throws com.vectorprint.VectorPrintException
        Description copied from class: AbstractFieldStyler
        calls AbstractFieldStyler.create() and AbstractFieldStyler.setFieldValues() and registers this FormFieldStyler as a PdfPCellEvent when element is null or when the DebuggablePdfPCell does not contain a BaseField yet. Subclasses should first call this style method and after this call AbstractFieldStyler.getFromCell(java.lang.Object) to get hold of the BaseField and style it. The BaseField is drawn on the PdfPTable.TEXTCANVAS of the cell.
        Specified by:
        style in interface BaseStyler
